MEDIA
personality Somizi Mhlongo’s reality show Living The Dream With Somizi had
viewers glued to their screens following the lifestyle of the star, his
dramatic antics, his personal lows and highs. Well, the good news is that it
returns next year in April for yet another riveting season. This was
announced today at the Dstv showcase in Randburg. It was also announced that
The Herd – a drama series based on a wealth hungry witch, who will do anything
or sacrifice anyone to attain wealth, will return for season 2 next year.
Winnie Ntshaba stars in the drama series as Mamngidi. Also, Lockdown will also
return for season 4, as will Uthandonethembu for season 3